caption.p: Estimated influenza-associated deaths per 100 000 people by influenza virus type and age. A, C and E shows estimated all-cause, respiratory or circulatory, and influenza or pneumonia deaths by influenza virus in under 65 years old group, respectively. B, D and F shows estimated all-cause, respiratory or circulatory, and influenza or pneumonia deaths by influenza virus in over 65 years old group, respectively. All estimated deaths are visualized by weekly estimated data.
